content: Fantastic app for tracking Commander games.

I used the free version for over a year and love it for its built in customization options and battery optimization. Functionally you're not missing out on really anything if you stick to the free version, but supporting the creator for a well made app was a no brainier to me. My wife and I actually use it these days for Star Realms so I set up the default table to load our names, favorite colors, and starting life count of 50.

Fantastic. Best counter on the market! Easy to use, great options for player customization. Does not drain battery! I have used a ton of these apps looking for the perfect one. This is it for all MTG players. Thank You!

I love this app, I never play magic without it anymore! I definantly reccomend this app to anyone who plays any form of magic. There's one bug I've noticed that would be awesome to be fixed though: if you have hide buttons by default enabled, then it won't let you go to the player customisation when click and holding on a players name.

This is THE best MTG EDH app there is. I would highly reccomend purchasing this edition and bring it to your next FNM. It helps you keep track of nearly anything you can think of in MTG (especially EDH) and all the themes you can choose from just help you immerse yourself in the game even more. The only thing is that I wish I could make a custom theme but with all the options, I'll be ok for now. KEEP UP THE GREAR WORK!!!
Is excellent.  needs to be updated w/recent banlist changes
replyContent: Just updated it! :) Thank you for your support, really!

content: this app is by far the best life tracker app on the market. they update frequently and the app has more ways to customize than most. I also really appreciate the incubation of a ban list in the app
replyContent: This kind of review warms my heart! Thanks a lot for your support!!
